      "name": "cli",
      "purpose": "Contains the marix-client-cli command-line binary entrypoint, which accepts --interactive or --oneshot \"request\" and drains Common streaming output plus Done completion events so oneshot completion exits promptly. It also connects the telemetry Logger to config.telemetry.server_address before starting the session."
